*** MemoServ Help - Command: SENDTO ***
Sends a memo to all users with equal or higher
access to the channel than the one specified.
 
Syntax:
/ms SENDTO #channel <VOP|HOP|AOP|SOP|CF> message
 
VOP will send a memo to all VOPs/HOPs/AOPs/SOPs/CFs.
 
HOP will send a memo to all HOPs/AOPs/SOPs/CFs.
 
AOP will send a memo to all AOPs/SOPs/CFs.
 
SOP will send a memo to all SOPs/CFs.
 
CF will send a memo to all Co-Founders.
 
Note: The channel founder will receive the memo from any selection.
 
Examples:
/ms SENDTO #IRCHelp VOP Congratulations to our new AOP, Miki!
/ms SENDTO #Italia SOP Please do not AOP anyone else.
 
Type /join #IRCHelp for more information.
*** End of Help ***
